scopes.name: schedule_only
scopes.explanation: The ISDA Schedule begins at line 36 with the heading 'SCHEDULE to the Master Agreement' and continues through all the 'Part' sections (Parts 1-5) and their subsections, ending with the execution block at line 269. The preceding lines are the standard pre-printed Master Agreement, and the following lines are the Confirmation and Schedule A, which are not part of the Schedule. This span contains only the negotiated Schedule provisions.
